1. sudo apt-get — purge remove postgresql
2. dpkg -l|grep postgres
3. sudo apt-get — purge remove pgdg-keyring postgresql*
4. sudo rm -rf /var/log/postgresql/
5. sudo rm -rf /var/lib/postgresql/
6. sudo rm -rf /etc/postgresql/
7. sudo deluser postgres
8. sudo delgroup postgres

How to remove pgAdmin 4 from Ubuntu 18.04.4 LTS
1.sudo apt autoremove pgadmin4
